s(107167)\">Isa. 40:3<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107768\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107768)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107768)\">Matt. 3:3<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108298\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108298)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108298)\">Mark 1:2-3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107947\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107947)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107947)\">Matt. 11:13-14<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108620\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108620)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108620)\">John 1:7-9<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107781\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107781)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107781)\">Matt. 3:11<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108305\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108305)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108305)\">Mark 1:4,7-8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">20. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109147\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109147)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109147)\">Acts 19:1-6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">21. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113603\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113603)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113603)\">D&amp;C 35:4<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">22. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106222\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106222)\">&nbsp;